creator: Weeloy Pte Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Weeloy Manager is exclusively designed for restaurant managers, who use Weeloy services, to monitor new reservations, bookings of the days, call logs and more.
Key Features:
Booking of the day
VIP notification
Call Control logs


About Weeloy,
Weeloy is a leading technology and eMarketing provider for restaurants across Singapore, Thailand, Hong Kong, Japan and Indonesia.
It is a one-stop, full-suite management platform for restaurants to manage reservations, tables, catering, online ordering and events marketing
B2B solutions including White Label Reservation System,Table Management Software, Booking Consolidation, Queue Management, Call Control and etc.

You can also visit www.weeloy.io for more information.
